name: 5x5 Cluster Variation (~13 min)
time_per_session_breakdown: 5 sets x ~30s work + 15s cluster rests + ~2 min rest/set => ~13 min total
overview_and_execution: Select a load you can do for ~6–7 reps. Perform 2 reps, rest 15s, 2 reps, rest 15s, 1 rep to reach 5 reps total. Rest 2–3 min, repeat for 5 total sets. Increase weight 2.5–5 lbs if all sets are done successfully.
example_application: Bench at 185 lbs (can do 7 reps). Do 2 reps, 15s rest, 2 reps, 15s rest, 1 rep = 1 set. Complete 5 sets. If you get all 25 reps, move to 190 lbs next time.
important_notes: Short rests help maintain power across all 5 reps. Keep technique consistent.
